name: McSwain Guitars Headstock Pendant
description: This is a 2-1/2 solid copper or brass McSwain Guitars headstock pendant that can be worn on a necklace or on a key chain.  ON SALE for the holidays.

name: Copper or Brass Skull Star
description:
This is a solid copper or brass skull star that can be attached to a necklace or key chain. Measures approx. 1" from tip to tip.

Please specify Brass or Copper

name: Sterling Silver Skull or .357 Magnum Bullet Star
description:
This is a solid sterling silver skull star that can be attached to a necklace or key chain. Measures approx. 1" from tip to tip.

Please specify which design: Skull or Bullet when ordering.

name: Brass, Copper or Aluminum .357 Magnum Bullet Star
description:
These are hand made metal stars in your choice of brass, copper, aircraft aluminum with a real .357 magnum bullet shell in the center.  They can easily be attached to a necklace or key chain.  Measure approx. 1" from tip to tip.

Please specify which metal when ordering.

Free shipping on Brass, Copper, Aluminum

name: D.S. Pendant
Mini-Motor Oil
description: McSwain Guitars is extremely proud to announce the arrival of the Mini Fuel Series.  Just like the original full sized McSwain Gasoline and Motor Oil Fuel Series guitars. Each "Mini-McSwain" stands approx. 8" tall.  These are great for collecting until you can get the "real deal."

name: Mini-Gasoline
description: McSwain Guitars is extremely proud to announce the arrival of the Mini Fuel Series.  Just like the original full sized McSwain Gasoline and Motor Oil Fuel Series guitars. Each "Mini-McSwain" stands approx. 8" tall.  These are great for collecting until you can get the "real deal."

name: Mini-Flame
description: McSwain Guitars is extremely proud to announce that Guitar Hero 5, released Sept. 2009, will feature several McSwain Guitar models.  McSwain has decided to offer a limited edition of "Mini McSwains" that are in the Guitar Hero 5 video game and are modeled after the original full sized McSwain guitars. Each "Mini-McSwain" stands approx. 8" tall.  These are great for collecting until you can get the "real deal."

name: Mini-Collection (pick any four designs)
description:
McSwain Guitars is extremely proud to announce that Guitar Hero 5, released Sept. 2009, will feature several McSwain Guitar models. McSwain has decided to offer a limited edition of "Mini McSwains" that are in the Guitar Hero 5 video game and are modeled after the original full sized McSwain guitars.  Each "Mini-McSwain" stands approx. 8" tall, and this set is for all the true collectors, containing all four of the Exclusive and Limited Edition run of the McSwain Minis.

Please specify in the notes of Paypal which four minis you want in the collection. You can choose from The Machine, Flame, Anarchy, Life, Gasoline and Motor Oil.
